NOTICE

This project is based on code from LatentQA, available at https://github.com/aypan17/latentqa, which is licensed under the Apache License 2.0.

Original Authors: Alexander Pan, Lijie Chen, and Jacob Steinhardt.
Original Paper: "LatentQA: Teaching LLMs to Decode Activations Into Natural Language" by Alexander Pan, Lijie Chen, and Jacob Steinhardt, published on arxiv.org in 2024.
DOI: https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.08686

The evaluation component for the FanToM dataset is adapted from https://github.com/skywalker023/fantom and implemented by Hyunwoo Kim, Melanie Sclar, Xuhui Zhou, Ronan Le Bras, Gunhee Kim, Yejin Choi, and Maarten Sap.

Modifications and additional contributions by Mohammadmahdi Jafari and the CRUISE Research Group at UNSW.